{"tid":1580476,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【既然無線cctvb報導開假新聞，點解唔報導埋假嘅天氣報告呢？】","createTime":"2019-09-19T05:51:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T06:05:32.000Z","uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"928160078c919b26af41fa22d1fff081a459af49","tid":1580476,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:51:56.000Z","msg":"【新聞為政权服務，同樣道理，天氣報告點解唔可以為政权服務呢？】<br />\n<br />\n1）香港篇<br />\n<br />\n例如中環有示威遊行，cctvb報香港天氣報告時，可以報假野，話未來中環有狂風、暴雨、落冰雹、行雷、颱風、地震、海嘯 ...<br />\n<br />\n天氣報告為政权服務。<br />\n如是者，想示威嘅人見到天氣惡劣成咁，咪唔會出街囉？<br />\n<br />\n點解cctvb會咁撚豬兜，咁都唔識做？"},{"pid":"93bb03dd216415173a33db2abe8fd522036c1c44","tid":1580476,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:52:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[公海 文宣 行動整合] 9.29全球抗赤納粹集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579667</a><br />\n全世界一齊對準ChiNazi極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZiskWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZiskWr.png&h=b85bf973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5f%2BqeKGcMvuhkm4gAZs5aLs%3D&h=3d929293\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5f%2BqeKGcMvuhkm4gAZs5aLs%3D&h=0846dff5\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ</a>"},{"pid":"c2b413baa4cb134e477a48fd1249cce4a51b20c0","tid":1580476,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:56:04.000Z","msg":"2）大灣區篇<br />\n<br />\n天氣報告為政权服務。<br />\n<br />\n為左昆外資同港資，托水投資落大灣區，其實cctvb可以報假天氣報告，一年三百六十五日都話大灣區四季如春，風調雨順。<br />\n<br />\n報導假嘅天氣報告，服務政权，咁先至係為阿爺跪低叩頭嘅好奴才嘛。<br />\n<br />\n點解咁簡單都唔識做？cctvb真係好撚豬兜。"},{"pid":"53209cc2f2233a8f8a6baa7e5473d8a7828eaba3","tid":1580476,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:04:58.000Z","msg":"3）一帶一路篇<br />\n<br />\n天氣報告為政权服務。<br />\n<br />\n為一帶一路國家報假嘅天氣報告，嗱，咁就麻煩小小。<br />\n<br />\n正路，肯加入一帶一路嘅國家，cctvb就話個D國家四季如春。明明狂風暴雨地震死人冧樓都好，都死口話陽光明媚，和風飄飄咁款。<br />\n<br />\n但如果唔加入一帶一路嘅國家，天氣報告就寫衰佢，話佢地震海嘯死人冧樓山崩洪水咁樣。<br />\n<br />\n但麻煩就麻煩就於政治嘅野，訊息萬變。<br />\n<br />\n例如意大利加入左一路一帶，咁肯定係報假新聞，話該地長期都天氣好好，和風暖日云云。<br />\n<br />\n但如果有日意大利時裝公司又辱華，咁個假嘅天氣報告點作呢？話天氣好好，定寫衰佢，話天氣好差呢？<br />\n<br />\n咁真係好考cctvb報假新聞條友個老鼠腦喇"},{"pid":"8182559399549482a375d5aef17fe8d5358256ac","tid":1580476,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:05:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">星期六 再光復屯門<br />\n星期日 機場4.0</span></strong></span>"}]}